{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"value"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ","text":"Equatable"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","text":"Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A value to monitor for changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"value"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"transform"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view whenever "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" changes."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Consider three identical views controlled by a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"button that changes all three simultaneously:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first view animates rotating the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The second uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to change the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“Rotation\\nModified” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" view animation by a factor of 2.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third uses the "},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to disable animations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"text":